=====================================
This is the rules of the game hangman
=====================================
The rules of this game are simple.
Type hmchal [user] [word] to start the
game. 

RULES:
1) You are only allowed real words
2) You are not allowed capital letters in your words
3) You are not allowed to use punctuation in words

The rest is obvious.

ByE bYe

from Horace



